headline: 1 Services Stock Worth Your Attention and 2 We Brush Off
summary: Business services providers thrive by solving complex operational challenges for their clients, allowing them to focus on their secret sauce. But increasing competition from AI-driven upstarts has tempered enthusiasm, limiting the industry’s gains to 13.5% over the past six months. This return lagged the S&P 500’s 15.9% climb.
